rows.label: tlk44400287_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Luxurian science has been passed
down for generations, so our knowledge
far surpasses the Superbians'.

rows.label: tlk44400287_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You are outlanders, if I'm not mistaken?
Then I must not let myself sound as if
we're blowing our own trumpets.

rows.label: tlk44400287_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Let me simply say that thanks to our
extensive collection of records, we are
able to address all manner of issues.
